      "title": "First the Speaker voted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Voting to elect someone for the vacant post of President has started in the Parliament since last 14th.",
        "The names of Members of Parliament Anurakumara Dissanayake, Dallas Alagaperuma and Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe were nominated yesterday.",
        "The empty ballot box is then displayed to the MPs by the Parliamentary Secretary and sealed."
      ],
